PLUSH shopping mall ­Princes Square wants ­visitors to get into the swing of things by entering a ­charity challenge. Swing by for golf fun in mall PLUSH shopping mall ­Princes Square wants ­visitors to get into the swing of things by entering a ­charity challenge.From Friday until Sunday, the centre has teamed up with Bunkered Magazine to transform its courtyard area into a golf green.Budding sports enthusiasts, aged six and over, will be encouraged to perfect their stance, practise their swing and take their &shy;winning shot.If successful in scoring a hole in one, they will receive a saltire flag golf head cover. 